    • deriveType

      public VerifiableCredentialType deriveType()
      Return the verifiable credential type. Sort of confusing in the specification. For sdjwt, we have a "vct" claim. See: https://openid.net/specs/openid-4-verifiable-credential-issuance-1_0.html#name-credential-request-6 For iso mdl (not yet supported) we have a "doctype" See: https://openid.net/specs/openid-4-verifiable-credential-issuance-1_0.html#name-credential-request-5 For jwt_vc and ldp_vc, we will be inferring from the "credential_definition" See: https://openid.net/specs/openid-4-verifiable-credential-issuance-1_0.html#name-credential-request-3
